Unless otherwise specified, this Code is applicable
throughout the Town of Newcastle as shown on the Town of
Newcastle Official District Map.

All departments, boards, and authorities of the Town of
Newcastle must comply with the procedural requirements
of this Code.

Real property used or occupied by the Town of Newcastle
is exempt from the standards of this Code.

Real property used or occupied by the State of Maine is
exempt from the standards of this Code.

This Code must apply to each new use, structure, activity,
or to an alteration, enlargement, or discontinued use of
a nonconforming use, structure, or activity on or after
effective date of this Code.

If a permit or approval is required under this Code, no earth
moving or construction may occur prior to obtaining that
permit or approval.

No activity, use, or structure contemplated by this Code
may be undertaken unless in conformity with this Code.
